Gripa Tombrapa bụ nwanyị Naijiria na-agba ịnyịnya ígwè. O ritere ihe nrite ọla edo mgbe ọ na-anọchite anya Naijiria na ihe omume ịgba ịnyịnya ígwè nke ụmụ nwanyị a na akpọ time trial n'akụkụ Happiness Okafor, Glory Odiase, na Rosemary Marcus na egwuregwu mba Afrika niile emere n'afọ 2015 na Congo Brazzaville
